OL,7,FFormer minister John Penrose has said
OL,8,Fpeople should be able to add more
OL,9,Fstoreys to their homes to tackle
OL,10,Fhousing shortages and warned that the
OL,11,Ffailure to build enough houses in the
OL,12,FUK has led to "increased poverty".
