OL,15,FBright Blue think-tank, shared
OL,16,Fexclusively with i, the former
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland minister warned that
OL,18,Fthe country's housing crisis had been
OL,19,F"brewing for ages" and that large-
OL,20,Fscale changes are needed to "upend
OL,21,Ffour or more decades of failure".
